Hi. I&#039;m Led Manville. One of my passions is music, doing it and djing it too. The bands i mix are mainly ebm, futurepop, industrial, synth, electro, trance, psy and gothic. I do harmonic mixing, so appart from beatmatching i try to fit also the melodies from one song to another.
I&#039;ve been djing since 20 years ago in many clubs and parties in Madrid.
